*christine-0.7.0 (15 Feb 2012)

  15 Feb 2012; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> +christine-0.7.0.ebuild,
  +files/christine-0.7.0-validate.patch:
  Version bump. Force at least Python >= 2.7 with USE="sqlite" enabled and use
  python.eclass wrt #313937 by Ian Delaney and Arfrever Frehtes Taifersar
  Arahesis.

  07 Jul 2011; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> christine-0.4.0.ebuild:
  Change away from deprecated python.eclass functions by Arfrever.

  28 May 2010; Arfrever Frehtes Taifersar Arahesis <arfrever@gentoo.org>
  christine-0.4.0.ebuild:
  Delete call to deprecated python_version().

  08 Sep 2009; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  christine-0.4.0.ebuild:
  dev-lang/python is required with USE sqlite wrt #284104, thanks to Arthur
  Spitzer.

